import { devFreeze } from "@rpldy/shared";
export const DEFAULT_PARAM_NAME = "file";
export const DEFAULT_FILTER = () => true;
export const DEFAULT_OPTIONS = devFreeze({
  autoUpload: true,
  clearPendingOnAdd: false,
  inputFieldName: "file",
  concurrent: false,
  maxConcurrent: 2,
  grouped: false,
  maxGroupSize: 5,
  method: "POST",
  params: {},
  fileFilter: DEFAULT_FILTER,
  forceJsonResponse: false,
  withCredentials: false,
  destination: {},
  send: null,
  sendWithFormData: true,
  formDataAllowUndefined: false,
  fastAbortThreshold: 100
});
